org.jdrupes.mdoclet

Class RootDocWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jdrupes.mdoclet.RootDocWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.sun.javadoc.Doc, com.sun.javadoc.DocErrorReporter, com.sun.javadoc.RootDoc, Comparable<Object>

    public class RootDocWrapper
extends Object
implements com.sun.javadoc.RootDoc

    A wrapper for the RootDoc. It forwards all calls to the original root document exception options(), which may contain a modified array of doclet options.
